Package: yieldmaps
Type: Package
Title: Create yield maps from raw points
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Luigi", "Ranghetti", 
                    email = "ranghetti.l@irea.cnr.it", 
                    role = c("aut", "cre"), 
                    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6207-5188")))
Description: This package contains functions used to import raw yield data,
 filter them, interpolate them and merge in order to produce raster yield maps.
 The package is under construction (alpha version).
